{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":520,"text":"I'm here to talk to you today"},{"time":2659,"text":"about a story that we have all\nbeen conditioned to believe"},{"time":5795,"text":"is not possible."},{"time":7359,"text":"It's a story about a living,\nbreathing start-up"},{"time":9681,"text":"flourishing in an unlikely environment:"},{"time":12100,"text":"the United States government."},{"time":13950,"text":"Now, this start-up is fundamentally\nbeginning to disrupt"},{"time":16608,"text":"the way government does\nbusiness from the inside out."},{"time":19120,"text":"But before I get there,\nlet's start with the problem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":21644,"text":"For me, the problem begins\nwith a number: 137."},{"time":25923,"text":"137 is the average number of days"},{"time":29441,"text":"a veteran has to wait to have benefits\nprocessed by the VA."},{"time":32876,"text":"137 days."},{"time":35032,"text":"Now, in order to file that application\nin the first place,"},{"time":37811,"text":"she has to navigate\nover 1,000 different websites"},{"time":41423,"text":"and over 900 different call-in numbers,"},{"time":44240,"text":"all owned and operated\nby the United States government."}]},{"cues":[{"time":48073,"text":"Now, we live in times\nof incredible change."},{"time":51266,"text":"The private sector is constantly changing"},{"time":53740,"text":"and improving itself all the time."},{"time":55529,"text":"For that matter, it's removing\nevery single inconvenience in my life"},{"time":58991,"text":"that I could possibly think of."},{"time":60808,"text":"I could be sitting on my couch\nin my apartment,"},{"time":63387,"text":"and from my phone, I can order\na warm, gluten-free meal"},{"time":66453,"text":"that can arrive at my door\nin less than 10 minutes."},{"time":69456,"text":"But meanwhile, a working mother\nwho depends on food stamps"},{"time":73703,"text":"to support her family"},{"time":75788,"text":"has to complete an arduous,\ncomplicated application"},{"time":78951,"text":"which she might not even\nbe able to do online."},{"time":81436,"text":"And the inability of her to do that same\nwork from her couch means"},{"time":85602,"text":"that she might be having to take\ndays or hours off of work"},{"time":88706,"text":"that she can't spare."},{"time":91173,"text":"And this growing dichotomy"},{"time":93713,"text":"between the beneficiaries\nof the tech revolution"},{"time":96031,"text":"and those it's left behind"},{"time":97450,"text":"is one of the greatest\nchallenges of our time --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":99996,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":105607,"text":"Because government's failure\nto deliver digital services that work"},{"time":109886,"text":"is disproportionately impacting\nthe very people who need it most."},{"time":114464,"text":"It's impacting the students\ntrying to go to college,"},{"time":117107,"text":"the single mothers\ntrying to get health care,"},{"time":119185,"text":"the veterans coming home from battle."},{"time":120986,"text":"They can't get what they need\nwhen they need it."},{"time":124082,"text":"And for these Americans,"},{"time":125492,"text":"government is more than just\na presidential election every four years."},{"time":129171,"text":"Government is a lifeline\nthat provides services they need"},{"time":132261,"text":"and depend on and deserve."},{"time":134610,"text":"Which is, quite frankly,"},{"time":135801,"text":"why government needs to get\nits shit together and catch up."},{"time":139008,"text":"Just saying."}]},{"cues":[{"time":140191,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":143950,"text":"Now, this wasn't always a problem\nI was passionate about."},{"time":146895,"text":"When I joined President Obama's\ncampaign in 2008,"},{"time":149679,"text":"we brought the tech industry's\nbest practices into politics."},{"time":152860,"text":"We earned more money,"},{"time":154615,"text":"we engaged more volunteers"},{"time":156360,"text":"and we earned more votes\nthan any political campaign in history."},{"time":160058,"text":"We were a cutting-edge start-up\nthat changed the game of politics forever."},{"time":163864,"text":"So when the President asked\na small group of us"},{"time":166147,"text":"to bring that very same disruption\ndirectly into government,"},{"time":169022,"text":"I knew it wasn't going to be easy work,"},{"time":170913,"text":"but I was eager and showed up\nready to get to work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":174791,"text":"Now, on my first day in DC,"},{"time":177465,"text":"my first day in government,"},{"time":179999,"text":"I walked into the office\nand they handed me a laptop."},{"time":182964,"text":"And the laptop was running Windows 98."}]},{"cues":[{"time":185448,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":186846,"text":"I mean, three entire presidential\nelections had come and gone"},{"time":190562,"text":"since the government had updated\nthe operating system on that computer."},{"time":193943,"text":"Three elections!"},{"time":196093,"text":"Which is when we realized"},{"time":197662,"text":"this problem was a whole lot bigger\nthan we ever could have imagined."},{"time":201750,"text":"Let me paint the picture for you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":204290,"text":"The federal government is the largest\ninstitution in the world."},{"time":208097,"text":"It spends over 86 billion dollars\na year -- 86 billion --"},{"time":212693,"text":"on federal IT projects."},{"time":214763,"text":"For context:"},{"time":215938,"text":"that is more than the entire\nventure capital industry spends"},{"time":218883,"text":"annually -- on everything."},{"time":221547,"text":"Now, the problem here"},{"time":223413,"text":"is that we the taxpayers\nare not getting what we pay for,"},{"time":227548,"text":"because 94 percent of federal IT projects"},{"time":231389,"text":"are over budget or behind schedule."},{"time":233628,"text":"94 percent!"},{"time":235088,"text":"For those of you keeping score,"},{"time":236601,"text":"yes, the number 94 is very close to 100."}]},{"cues":[{"time":238934,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":241045,"text":"There's another problem:"},{"time":242624,"text":"40 percent of those never end up\nseeing the light of day."},{"time":246412,"text":"They are completely scrapped or abandoned."},{"time":249014,"text":"Now, this is a very existentially\npainful moment for any organization,"},{"time":253796,"text":"because it means as government\ncontinues to operate"},{"time":256217,"text":"as it's programmed to do,"},{"time":257456,"text":"failure is nearly inevitable."},{"time":259482,"text":"And when the status quo\nis the riskiest option,"},{"time":262970,"text":"that means there is simply no other choice"},{"time":265042,"text":"than radical disruption."}]},{"cues":[{"time":268039,"text":"So, what do we do about it?"},{"time":270733,"text":"How do we fix this?"},{"time":273065,"text":"Well, the irony of all of this"},{"time":275706,"text":"is that we actually don't have to look\nany further than our backyard,"},{"time":279003,"text":"because right here in America\nare the very ideas, the very people,"},{"time":282892,"text":"who have swept our world\ninto a radically different place"},{"time":285586,"text":"than it was two decades ago."},{"time":287276,"text":"So what would it look like"},{"time":289581,"text":"if it was actually as easy to get\nstudent loans or veterans' benefits"},{"time":292945,"text":"as it is to order cat food to my house?"},{"time":296358,"text":"What would it look like"},{"time":298628,"text":"if there was an easy pathway\nfor the very entrepreneurs and innovators"},{"time":302585,"text":"who have disrupted our tech sector"},{"time":304372,"text":"to come and disrupt their government?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":306989,"text":"Well, my friends,\nhere's where we get to talk"},{"time":309143,"text":"about some of the exciting\nnew formulas we've discovered"},{"time":311814,"text":"for creating change in government."},{"time":313511,"text":"Enter the United States Digital Service."},{"time":316329,"text":"The United States Digital Service\nis a new network of start-ups,"},{"time":319823,"text":"a team of teams,"},{"time":321402,"text":"organizing themselves across government\nto create radical change."},{"time":326352,"text":"The mission of the United States\nDigital Service is to help government"},{"time":329699,"text":"deliver world-class digital services"},{"time":331811,"text":"for students, immigrants,\nchildren, the elderly -- everybody --"},{"time":336364,"text":"at dramatically lower costs."},{"time":339664,"text":"We are essentially trying to build\na more awesome government,"},{"time":343163,"text":"for the people, by the people, today."},{"time":345288,"text":"We don't care -- (Applause) Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347162,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":349378,"text":"Who doesn't want a more\nawesome government, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":352632,"text":"We don't care about politics."},{"time":355154,"text":"We care about making\ngovernment work better,"},{"time":357368,"text":"because it's the only one we've got."}]},{"cues":[{"time":359454,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":361883,"text":"Now, you can think of our team --\nwell, it's pretty funny --"},{"time":365130,"text":"you can think\nof our team a little bit like"},{"time":367206,"text":"the Peace Corps meets DARPA\nmeets SEAL Team 6."},{"time":370316,"text":"We're like the Peace Corps for nerds,"},{"time":372103,"text":"but instead of traveling to crazy,\ninteresting, far-off places,"},{"time":375100,"text":"you spend a lot of time indoors,\nbehind computers,"},{"time":377513,"text":"helping restore the fabric\nof our democracy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":379782,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":381859,"text":"Now, this team -- our playbook\nfor the United States Digital Service"},{"time":386197,"text":"is pretty simple."},{"time":388053,"text":"The first play is we recruit\nthe very best talent"},{"time":391681,"text":"our country has to offer,"},{"time":393418,"text":"and recruit them for short tours\nof duty inside government."},{"time":396447,"text":"These are the very people who have helped\nbuild the products and companies"},{"time":399973,"text":"that have made our tech sector amongst\nthe most innovative in the world."},{"time":403380,"text":"Second, we pair these incredible\npeople from the tech core"},{"time":406573,"text":"with the dedicated civil servants\nalready inside government"},{"time":409463,"text":"on the ground creating change."},{"time":411605,"text":"Third, we strategically deploy them\nin a targeted formation"},{"time":415515,"text":"at the most mission-critical,\nlife-changing, important services"},{"time":418699,"text":"that government offers."},{"time":420230,"text":"And finally, we give them\nmassive air cover,"},{"time":422897,"text":"from the leadership inside the agencies"},{"time":424796,"text":"all the way up to the President himself,"},{"time":427186,"text":"to transform these services\nfor the better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":430437,"text":"Now, this team is beginning to disrupt"},{"time":433276,"text":"how government does business\nfrom the inside out."},{"time":436538,"text":"If you study classic\npatterns of disruption,"},{"time":439569,"text":"one very common pattern is rather simple."},{"time":442252,"text":"It's to take something that has become\nroutine and standard in one industry"},{"time":445879,"text":"and apply it to another\nwhere it's a radical departure"},{"time":448443,"text":"from the status quo."},{"time":449736,"text":"Think about what Airbnb took\nthat was normal from hospitality"},{"time":453076,"text":"and revolutionized my apartment."},{"time":456058,"text":"The United States Digital Service\nis doing exactly that."},{"time":458948,"text":"We are taking what Silicon Valley\nand the private sector has learned"},{"time":462266,"text":"through a ton of hard work"},{"time":463592,"text":"about how to build\nplanetary-scale digital services"},{"time":466227,"text":"that delight users at lower cost,"},{"time":468115,"text":"and we're applying that to government,"},{"time":469979,"text":"where it is a radical departure\nfrom the status quo."}]},{"cues":[{"time":472899,"text":"Now, the good news is:"},{"time":475416,"text":"it's starting to work."},{"time":477768,"text":"We know this because we can\nalready see the results"},{"time":480222,"text":"from some of our early projects,\nlike the rescue effort of Healthcare.gov,"},{"time":483883,"text":"when that went off the rails."},{"time":485497,"text":"Fixing Healthcare.gov was the first place\nthat we ran this play,"},{"time":489225,"text":"and today we are taking that same play"},{"time":491106,"text":"and scaling it across a large number"},{"time":492876,"text":"of government's most important\ncitizen-facing services."},{"time":497077,"text":"Now, if I can take a moment"},{"time":499348,"text":"and brag about the team for a second --"},{"time":501475,"text":"it is the highest\nconcentration of badasses"},{"time":504086,"text":"I could have ever dreamed of."},{"time":506314,"text":"We have top talent from Google,\nFacebook, Amazon, Twitter and the likes,"},{"time":510166,"text":"all on staff today,"},{"time":512351,"text":"all choosing to join their government."},{"time":515699,"text":"And what's incredible is,"},{"time":516963,"text":"everybody is as eager and kind\nas they are intelligent."},{"time":520922,"text":"And I might add, by the way,\nover half of us are women."}]},{"cues":[{"time":524406,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":531244,"text":"The best way to understand this strategy"},{"time":533607,"text":"is actually to walk through\na couple of examples"},{"time":535891,"text":"of how it's working out in the wild."},{"time":537645,"text":"I'm going to give you\ntwo examples quickly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":539681,"text":"The first one is about immigration."},{"time":541986,"text":"This, my friends, is your typical\nimmigration application."},{"time":545625,"text":"Yes, you guessed it --"},{"time":546812,"text":"it's almost entirely paper-based."},{"time":549310,"text":"In the best case,"},{"time":550485,"text":"the application takes about six\nto eight months to process."},{"time":553317,"text":"It is physically shipped thousands\nof miles -- thousands of miles! --"},{"time":557174,"text":"between no less than six\nprocessing centers."},{"time":560188,"text":"Now, little story:"},{"time":562168,"text":"about a decade ago,"},{"time":563343,"text":"the government thought\nthat if it brought this system online,"},{"time":566244,"text":"it could save taxpayer dollars\nand provide a better service,"},{"time":569142,"text":"which was a great idea."},{"time":570317,"text":"So, the typical government process began."},{"time":573922,"text":"Six years and 1.2 billion dollars later,"},{"time":578287,"text":"no working product was delivered --"},{"time":580592,"text":"1.2 billion with a \"B.\""},{"time":583480,"text":"Now at this point, the agency responsible,"},{"time":586046,"text":"US Citizenship and Immigration Services,"},{"time":587993,"text":"could have kept pouring money\ninto the failing program."},{"time":590781,"text":"Sadly, that's what often happens."},{"time":592448,"text":"That's the status quo today."},{"time":594075,"text":"But they didn't."},{"time":595260,"text":"The dedicated civil servants\ninside the agency"},{"time":597502,"text":"decided to stand up and call for change."},{"time":599825,"text":"We deployed a small team\nof just six people,"},{"time":602497,"text":"and what many people don't know is"},{"time":604203,"text":"that's the same size as the rescue\neffort of Healthcare.gov --"},{"time":607158,"text":"just six people."},{"time":608403,"text":"And that team jumped in, side-by-side,"},{"time":610258,"text":"to support the agency\nin transitioning this project"},{"time":612996,"text":"into more modern business practices,\nmore modern development practices."},{"time":617216,"text":"Now, in non-tech speak,"},{"time":618405,"text":"what that basically means\nis taking big, multi-year projects"},{"time":622411,"text":"and breaking them up\ninto bite-sized chunks,"},{"time":624750,"text":"so that way we can reduce the risk"},{"time":626410,"text":"and actually start to see results\nevery couple of weeks,"},{"time":629071,"text":"instead of waiting\nin a black box for years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":631256,"text":"So within less than three months\nof our team being on the ground,"},{"time":634486,"text":"we were already able to push\nour first products to production."},{"time":638152,"text":"The first one, this is the form I-90."},{"time":640788,"text":"This is used to file\nfor your replacement green card."},{"time":644208,"text":"Now, for immigrant visa holders,"},{"time":645797,"text":"a replacement green card is a big deal."},{"time":648709,"text":"Your green card is your proof\nof identification,"},{"time":650991,"text":"it's your work authorization,"},{"time":652404,"text":"it's the proof that you can\nbe here in this country."},{"time":654877,"text":"So waiting six months while the government\nprocesses the replacement"},{"time":658122,"text":"is not cool."},{"time":659346,"text":"I'm excited to tell you that today,"},{"time":661061,"text":"you can now, for the first time,\nfile for a replacement green card"},{"time":664242,"text":"entirely online without anyone\ntouching a piece of paper."},{"time":667469,"text":"It is faster, it is cheaper,"},{"time":669511,"text":"and it's a better user experience\nfor the applicant"},{"time":671932,"text":"and the government employees alike."}]},{"cues":[{"time":673844,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":680677,"text":"Another one, quickly."},{"time":681852,"text":"Last fall, we just released\na brand-new practice civics test."},{"time":685123,"text":"So as part of becoming a US citizen,"},{"time":687387,"text":"you have to pass a civics test."},{"time":689761,"text":"For anyone who has taken this test,\nit can be quite the stressful process."},{"time":694123,"text":"So our team released a very easy,\nsimple-to-use tool in plain language"},{"time":698734,"text":"to help people prepare,"},{"time":700914,"text":"to help ease their nerves,"},{"time":702612,"text":"to help them feel more confident"},{"time":704366,"text":"in taking the next step\nin pursuing their American dream."},{"time":707821,"text":"Because all of this work,\nall of this work on immigration,"},{"time":710756,"text":"is about taking complicated processes\nand making them more human."}]},{"cues":[{"time":715527,"text":"The other day, one of the dedicated\ncivil servants on the ground"},{"time":718581,"text":"said something incredibly profound."},{"time":721483,"text":"She said that she's never been\nthis hopeful or optimistic"},{"time":724730,"text":"about a project in her entire\ntime in government."},{"time":728101,"text":"And she's been doing this for 30 years."},{"time":731285,"text":"That is exactly the kind of hope\nand culture change"},{"time":733730,"text":"we are trying to create."}]},{"cues":[{"time":735435,"text":"For my second example, I want to bring\nit back to veterans for a second,"},{"time":738943,"text":"and what we are doing to build them a VA"},{"time":740917,"text":"that is worthy of their service\nand their sacrifice."},{"time":744129,"text":"I'm proud to say\nthat just a few months ago,"},{"time":746321,"text":"we released a brand-new beta"},{"time":748241,"text":"of a new website, Vets.gov."},{"time":750920,"text":"Vets.gov is a simple, easy-to-use website"},{"time":752929,"text":"that brings all of the online services\na veteran needs into one place."},{"time":756689,"text":"One website, not thousands."},{"time":760166,"text":"The site is a work in progress,\nbut it's significant progress,"},{"time":763189,"text":"because it's designed\nwith the users who matter most:"},{"time":765800,"text":"the veterans themselves."},{"time":767729,"text":"This might sound incredibly obvious,\nbecause it should be,"},{"time":770546,"text":"but sadly, this isn't\nnormal for government."},{"time":772792,"text":"Far too often, product decisions\nare made by committees of stakeholders"},{"time":776260,"text":"who do their best to represent\nthe interests of the user,"},{"time":778966,"text":"but they're not necessarily\nthe users themselves."},{"time":781294,"text":"So our team at the VA went out,\nwe looked at the data,"},{"time":783859,"text":"we talked to veterans themselves"},{"time":785547,"text":"and we started simple and small,"},{"time":787159,"text":"with the two most important services\nthat matter most to them:"},{"time":790567,"text":"education benefits\nand disability benefits."},{"time":793873,"text":"I'm proud to say that they are\nlive on the site today,"},{"time":796541,"text":"and as the team continues\nto streamline more services,"},{"time":799103,"text":"they will be ported over here,\nand the old sites, shut down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":801978,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":807596,"text":"To me, this is what change\nlooks like in 2016."}]},{"cues":[{"time":812493,"text":"When you walk out of the Oval Office,"},{"time":814291,"text":"the first time I was ever\nthere, I noticed a quote"},{"time":816656,"text":"the President had embroidered on the rug."},{"time":818647,"text":"It's the classic JFK quote."},{"time":820576,"text":"It says, \"No problem of human destiny\nis beyond human beings.\""},{"time":825882,"text":"It's true."},{"time":827256,"text":"We have the tools to solve these problems."},{"time":830423,"text":"We have the tools to come together\nas a society, as a country,"},{"time":833732,"text":"and to fix this together."},{"time":836073,"text":"Yes, it's hard."},{"time":838034,"text":"It's particularly hard\nwhen we have to fight,"},{"time":840161,"text":"when we have to refuse to succumb\nto the belief that things won't change."},{"time":844626,"text":"But in my experience,"},{"time":846380,"text":"it's often the hardest things\nthat are the most worth doing,"},{"time":849864,"text":"because if we don't do them,"},{"time":851693,"text":"who will?"},{"time":853130,"text":"This is on us,"},{"time":855162,"text":"all of us, together,"},{"time":857082,"text":"because government is not\nan abstract institution or a concept."},{"time":860686,"text":"Our government is us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":863790,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":868541,"text":"Today, it is no longer a question"},{"time":870614,"text":"of if change is possible."},{"time":873422,"text":"The question is not, \"Can we?\""},{"time":876367,"text":"The question is, \"Will we?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":878912,"text":"Will you?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":880316,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":881508,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":885120,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":886334,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}